trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en samling av <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: Use the StyleCollection class to store and manage <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style> objects for a control.
trans-unit.target: Bruk StyleCollection-klasse for å lagre og behandle <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style>objekter for en kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style>

trans-unit.source: Control developers can use this class to contain a set of styles that apply to different portions of the control.
trans-unit.target: Kontrollutviklere kan bruke denne klassen inneholder et sett med stiler som gjelder for forskjellige deler av kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The collection dynamically increases in size as objects are added.
trans-unit.target: Samlingen øker dynamisk i størrelsen som er lagt til objekter.

trans-unit.source: Indexes in this collection are zero-based.
trans-unit.target: Indekser i denne samlingen er null.

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.Count%2A> property to determine how many objects are in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Bruk av <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.Count%2A>til å fastslå hvor mange objekter er i samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.Count%2A>

trans-unit.source: Additionally, use the StyleCollection methods and properties to provide the following functionality: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.StyleCollection.Add%2A> method to add a single style to the collection.
trans-unit.target: I tillegg bruke StyleCollection metodene og egenskapene til å gi følgende funksjonalitet: - <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.StyleCollection.Add%2A>metode for å legge til én mal-samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.StyleCollection.Add%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.StyleCollection.Insert%2A> method to add a style at a particular index within the collection.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.StyleCollection.Insert%2A>Metoden legges til en stil for en bestemt indeks i samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.StyleCollection.Insert%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.StyleCollection.Remove%2A> method to remove a style from the collection.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.StyleCollection.Remove%2A>Metode for å fjerne en stil fra samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.StyleCollection.Remove%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.StyleCollection.RemoveAt%2A> method to remove the style located at a particular index.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.StyleCollection.RemoveAt%2A>Metode for å fjerne stilen plassert på en bestemt indeks.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.StyleCollection.RemoveAt%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.StyleCollection.Contains%2A> method to determine whether a particular style is already in the collection.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.StyleCollection.Contains%2A>Metode for å finne ut om en bestemt stil er allerede i samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.StyleCollection.Contains%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.StyleCollection.IndexOf%2A> method to retrieve the index of a style within the collection.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.StyleCollection.IndexOf%2A>Metode for å hente indeksen for en stil i samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.StyleCollection.IndexOf%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.Clear%2A> method to remove all the styles from the collection.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.Clear%2A>Metode for å fjerne alle stiler fra samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.Clear%2A>

trans-unit.source: Copies the elements of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.StyleCollection"></xref> to a one-dimensional <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style"></xref> array, starting at the specified index of the target array.

trans-unit.target: Stilelementene kopieres til det <xref:System.Array>objektet i samme rekkefølge som de er indeksert i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.StyleCollection>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.StyleCollection> </xref:System.Array>

trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Array>som er målet for kopierte stiler.</xref:System.Array>

trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Array>må ha nullbasert indeksering.</xref:System.Array>

Because the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.StyleCollection.GetKnownTypes*> method of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.StyleCollection"></xref> returns a list with only one type, the input `index` is ignored.
